IFrame: 

1. An iframe (Inline Frame) is an HTML element used to embed another webpage inside the current webpage 
        In short its webpage inside another page
2. iframe has a separate DOM context from the main page so we can not directly access it with page.locator(#locator)

IFrame Handling:
Iframes handled with 2 ways, first is "FrameLocator" and another is frame object i.e page.frame

FrameLocator: 
frameLocator() is a Playwright method used to locate and interact with elements inside an iframe.

How to handle with FrameLocator:
1. Locate iframe using frameLocator --- const frame123 = await page.frameLocator("Locator of iframe")
2. Then locate elements inside it   --- const text  = await frame123.locator(#locator).textContent()


Frame Object i.e page.frame:
It works with only frame properties like frame "name" and frame "url". 
<iframe id="frame1" src="/rahulshetty/"></iframe>
const frame = page.frame({ name: "frame1" });  ----get Frame by Name
const frame = page.frame({ url: /rahulshetty/ }); ---get Frame by URL


Difference:
frameLocator()	                                       frame()
Uses selectors id/class/xpath                          Uses frame properties i.e name & url            
Locator based	                                       Frame object based
page.frameLocator()Returns FrameLocator object         page.frame() Returns a Frame object.


Q1: Why is frameLocator preferred over frame()?

Answer:
frameLocator() provides:

automatic waiting
cleaner chaining
better readability
improved stability
It is Playwright’s modern recommended approach for iframe handling.


==Interview Best Answer==

*frameLocator() is preferred for modern Playwright UI automation because it provides automatic waiting, 
cleaner syntax, and better stability for iframe interactions.
*frame() is mainly used for advanced frame-level operations like iterating frames, accessing frame metadata, 
or handling dynamically identified frames.


Q2: What are common iframe issues?
Timeout Error

Cause:
Wrong iframe locator
Element not visible
Trying from main page
Strict Mode Violation >> Cause: Multiple matching elements
